{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"24300f2f0b","title":"“人民代表大会是表决机器”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f064e040e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"24300f2f0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7e3466b684","name":"李亚铃"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"8cfe777b5e","name":"郭成兴"},{"id":"d05847b78e","name":"孙增垣"},{"id":"ec445d94b0","name":"蔡荣荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5d1cdb7201","type":"title","text":"“人民代表大会是表决机器”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"70c793b288","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院蔡荣荣郭成兴李亚铃孙增垣","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"c1415fcebe","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡荣荣说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"b2cada7d55","type":"paragraph","text":"「人民代表大会是表决机器，没有真正起到最高权力机关的作用。」「人民代表大会所讨论的内容，甚至很小的具体问题，如年度计划都由党中央提出，应该由有关部门提出，否则就是以党代政了，党中央只能从总的方向，方针政策上提出意见……」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"7404bd32a3","type":"paragraph","text":"郭成兴说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"5c6d490b98","type":"paragraph","text":"「我国人民代表大会能否代表人民利益？」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"47317af930","type":"paragraph","text":"李亚铃在一篇〈当了人民代表代表谁〉的文章中，说他当了半年的人民代表，还不知道干些什么，他的代表是怎样产生的，说组织上既没向群众宣布，又不给指示工作。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"671ab26377","type":"paragraph","text":"孙增垣说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"57cc558ae9","type":"paragraph","text":"「宪法是一本粉饰太平，在国际上吹嘘、而实际上并没有付诸实现的一张毫无实际意义的空头支票，人权方面没有实际的保证。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"},{"id":"fce2e957f8","type":"paragraph","text":"「人民代表视察工作，是表面一套，做个样子，只说好，不说坏。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b"}],"page":{"id":"87c5fed635","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"24300f2f0b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}